{"tid":1187794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[下]梁美芬稱律師會立場書太遲公布　意見難發揮作用","createTime":"2019-06-06T01:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T02:34:30.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f395981ae4289f524110c9c9f8bd94984129b5a1","tid":1187794,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"律師會就修訂《逃犯條例》發表立場書，建議擴大本港法院域外法權，處理包括謀殺和誤殺等嚴重罪行。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員梁美芬說，律師會的立場書太遲公布，意見難以發揮作用。<br />\n<br />\n她又認為，域外法權並不可取，會改變屬地原則，移交逃犯方式，應該類似其他已簽署長期協議的司法管轄區，絕大部分國家都不會以域外法權方式，處理逃犯移交。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬指出，政府已作兩次重大讓步，包括加入公平審訊等人權保障，法庭審訊時，亦可考慮政府啟動時有否提出有關措施，她對律師會的立場書不夠聚焦最新情況，感到可惜。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461167-20190605.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461167-20190605.htm&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=2a80e85d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461167-20190605.htm&h=042e941b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461167-20190605.htm</a>"},{"pid":"db989b2a368607f6f692c330006df6c5ff3f708a","tid":1187794,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:16:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0uQ23FovmEc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0uQ23FovmEc&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=c33178b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0uQ23FovmEc</a><br />\n有啲人讀狗屎法律"},{"pid":"363382a3122173a97903d35969ea230d8364810a","tid":1187794,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530c3db57c3896ed505d4fbfec4acad34a2f9b03","tid":1187794,"uid":218729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f395981ae4289f524110c9c9f8bd94984129b5a1","tid":1187794,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"律師會就修訂《逃犯條例》發表立場書，建議擴大本港法院域外法權，處理包括謀殺和誤殺等嚴重罪行。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員梁美芬說，律師會的立場書太遲公布，意見難以發揮作用。<br />\n<br />\n她又認為，域外法權並不可取，會改變屬地原則，移交逃犯方式，應該類似其他已簽署長期協議的司法管轄區，絕大部分國家都不會以域外法權方式，處理逃犯移交。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬指出，政府已作兩次重大讓步，包括加入公平審訊等人權保障，法庭審訊時，亦可考慮政府啟動時有否提出有關措施，她對律師會的立場書不夠聚焦最新情況，感到可惜。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461167-20190605.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461167-20190605.htm&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElmaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=2a80e85d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461167-20190605.htm&h=042e941b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461167-20190605.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T02:34:30.000Z","msg":"11哥奶成咁，我明，身有屎無辦法<br />\n但係梁美芬其實點解會投共到咁核突"}]}